+                        人工智能对现代创作者的影响：一场关于主权的争夺战
+                    </h1>
+<!-- Hero Image -->
+<div class="mb-16 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-low aspect-[16/9]">
+<img alt="AI and Creativity" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" data-alt="Abstract cinematic composition of ethereal digital light particles forming a human hand touching a glowing neural network mesh in a dark studio" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCwUESnv5GhdDxBkxJAxN2v73vqstZEKOqkY8l2TSyp3OOoi57yg8YD7tMNpcUqsSXwdsWHBybIdFOPbt3leHWGf_ZpytPKzn5neRYjKgzk5c-HOOODOC_XUfWMPXmGaY1izs5hvSyugFlQKkIJrkgB0sCPlJIsxOfADLyteYbH9L2IcN3676YMQ7XfbQzXefpeYxvLrnCrCIEy9dNOJHYmW9MvWB1eVahtsryQ5_KwYS9CiZZHKbYn9pVg4CIwDX_r_4_3X-keNQI"/>
